text:
BARTENDER
I told you, you're not welcome here.
You're not welcome anywhere.
Now, get the f*** out of my bar.

LOGAN
Just give me one more drink
and then I'll leave.

DEADPOOL
Hi, peanut.

I'm going to need you
to come with me right now.

LOGAN
Look, lady, I'm not interested.

DEADPOOL
Alright, well, I'm sort of

on the tick-tick,
so upsy-daisy, here we go.

LOGAN
Whoa, hey, hey!

DEADPOOL
Oh.

Whiskey dick of the claws.
It's quite common in Wolverines over 40.

LOGAN
You don't want this.

DEADPOOL
Unless you want to take a deep breath

through your f****** forehead,
I suggest you reconsider.

DEADPOOL
I'm about to lose everything
that I've ever cared about.

WOLVERINE
Not my f****** problem.

DEADPOOL
Is that what you said when your world
went to s***?

WOLVERINE
Come again?

PARADOX
This Wolverine let down his entire world.

WADE WILSON
Want to talk about what's haunting you,

or should we wait
for a third act flashback?

WOLVERINE
Uh, go f*** yourself.

DEADPOOL
I don't know anything about saving worlds,
but you do!

WOLVERINE
Trust me, kid, I'm no hero.

WADE WILSON
You were an X-Man.

WADE WILSON
You were the X-Man.

DEADPOOL
I am soaking wet right now.
Boys are so silly.

DEADPOOL
This is what I'm talking about.

DEADPOOL
Big slow motion action sequence!

DEADPOOL
Who knows if you live or die?

DEADPOOL
Let's f****** go!

WOLVERINE
Let's f****** go.

DEADPOOL
Yeah!

BLIND AL
Wanna do some c******?

WADE WILSON
Hey!

C****** is the one thing
that Feige said is off limits.

BLIND AL
What about Bolivian marching powder?

WADE WILSON
They know all the slang terms.
They have a list.

BLIND AL
Even snowboarding?

WADE WILSON
Even disco dust.

BLIND AL
White Girl, Interrupted?

WADE WILSON
Even Forrest Bump.

BLIND AL
Do you want to build a snowman?

WADE WILSON
Yes! But I can't!
